Uses of Package
com.stremebase.dal

  • Packages that use com.stremebase.dal 
    Package Description
    com.stremebase.dal
    com.stremebase.dal is the Data Access Layer (along with the fields).
    com.stremebase.field
    com.stremebase.field offers some basic high-level fields to be used at the data access layer.
  • Classes in com.stremebase.dal used by com.stremebase.dal 
    Class and Description
    Cursor
    Cursor is the result of a database query
    Cursor.BasicCursor
    The normal not-bigData -cursor, used when search result fits into main memory
    Field
    The abstract base class for fields.
    Table
    Table is container for all fields that share common key (belong to the same database entity).
    TableRelation
    Relates keys from two tables.
